## Using the service
using-service.heading=Using this service
using-service.should-be-able=This service is run by HM Revenue and Customs (HMRC). We want as many people as possible to be able to use this service. This means you should be able to:
using-service.bullet1=change colours, contrast levels and fonts
using-service.bullet2=zoom in up to 300% without the text spilling off the screen
using-service.bullet3=get from the start of the service to the end using just a keyboard
using-service.bullet4=get from the start of the service to the end using speech recognition software
using-service.bullet5=listen to the service using a screen reader (including the most recent versions of JAWS, NVDA and VoiceOver)
using-service.simple-text=We have also made the text in the service as simple as possible to understand.
using-service.making-device-easier.part1=AbilityNet has advice
using-service.making-device-easier.part2=' on making your device easier to use if you have a disability.'

